Watchlist

Where to Watch

Renee Zellweger won a Golden Globe for her hilarious performance in this dark comedy. She plays a soap-opera-obsessed waitress who loses her grip on reality after witnessing a murder. Then, she goes in search of her true love: a fictional TV doctor. Morgan Freeman, Chris Rock, Greg Kinnear. Directed by Neil LaBute ("Your Friends and Neighbors")
